            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>nvicto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>ithrae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>PPP</abbr><ex>ublii</ex></expan> Aelii Nepos et <lb n="3"/>Proculus et Firminus <lb n="4"/>pro salute sua suorumque
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift ist oberhalb eines gleichfalls in den Fels gehauenen Mithrasreliefs eingemeißelt; Maße des Inschriftfeldes: 40 x 111 cm. (B): CIMRM 1483: Z. 2: d(omino) P(ublius) P(ublii) Aelii Nepos et; Selem: Z. 2: d(---) P(ublius) P(ublii) Aelii Nepos et; Z. 3: Proclus e(t).</p>
            </div>
